788
01:25:15,840 --> 01:25:17,717
'body and soul,

789
01:25:17,800 --> 01:25:19,916
'til death do us part!'

790
01:25:38,720 --> 01:25:41,439
'Nothing can stop us now.

791
01:25:41,520 --> 01:25:44,034
'Resistance is impossible.

792
01:25:44,120 --> 01:25:47,635
'It is a new world order

793
01:25:47,720 --> 01:25:50,678
'and we are in control.

794
01:25:53,600 --> 01:25:56,353
Come on, Joyce, I gotta get you out of here.

795
01:25:57,400 --> 01:25:59,994
That wouldn't be a very good idea, Alex.

796
01:26:00,080 --> 01:26:04,870
