805
01:27:58,960 --> 01:28:02,589
'Sweet, sweet revenge.

806
01:28:03,480 --> 01:28:06,756
'A dish best served cold.'

807
01:28:07,360 --> 01:28:09,794
But some like it hot.

808
01:28:10,640 --> 01:28:14,872
