before I'm through.

809
01:28:16,360 --> 01:28:18,476
Give it a rest, Helena.

810
01:28:21,200 --> 01:28:24,351
You always wanted to hog my glory,
didn't you?

811
01:28:24,440 --> 01:28:27,318
