812
01:28:32,560 --> 01:28:33,959
I never did.

813
01:28:34,040 --> 01:28:36,156
Liar!

814
01:29:05,920 --> 01:29:09,435
You pathetic weakling.

815
01:30:10,440 --> 01:30:11,998
Alex!

